      <h1>Concepts</h1>
      <h2>Cloudbox</h2>
      <p>A generated work computer grounded in a persona, containing files, artifacts, collaborators, run history, and retrospective lessons.</p>
      <h2>Dependency graph</h2>
      <p>Files are generated in topological order so downstream memos, decks, and PDFs can refer back to source packets and models.</p>
      <h2>Simulation</h2>
      <p>The work loop restores context each day, reads files, creates deliverables, contacts collaborators, and records activity history.</p>
